              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 2:",
                  "bold": true,
                  "underline": true
                },
                {
                  "text": " In the application form, fill in all the mandatory fields, paste the passport-sized photograph (signed across, if required), and attach copies of all the mandatory documents (self-attest, if required)."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 3:",
                  "bold": true,
                  "underline": true
                },
                {
                  "text": " Submit the duly filled and signed application form along with the documents, within the prescribed period (if any), to the "
                },
                {
                  "text": "Member Secretary, Kala Academy, Panaji, Goa",
